a biography of mao and an account of china under his rule. red china blues: my long march from mao to now by jan wong, a reporter for the globe and mail of toronto, canada. the book describes her experiences as one of the first foreign exchange students to study in china after the cultural revolution and her life and experiences as a reporter in china until the mid 1990s. cinema[edit] bernardo bertolucci - the last emperor (1987) zhang yimou - raise the red lantern (1991) chen kaige - farewell my concubine (1993) zhang yimou - to live (1994) wu 